      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AWHOLELOTOFPRETTY (2) had a tough draw on the back row last start so did well to be beaten only 4.5 metres. Had been racing consistently prior and is much better served by this barrier. AMILLION PROMISES (3) led from a similar barrier to this when he scored at this circuit and distance two starts ago before drawing wider when third at his latest appearance. Has the benefit of a good draw so could give this a mighty shake. PARIS PRINCESS (5) started favourite last start but had to race wide and work. Won at this circuit and distance prior so is worth another chance. MAJOR MICKEY (7) placed here two back and did a good job to come from a wide barrier for fifth at Newcastle last time out.",
